erials associated with emergency preparedness plans.", "TaskType": "Core", "task_importance_score": 4.36, "penetration": 0.0}, {"ONETSOCCode": "11-9161", "Task": "Develop instructional materials for the public and make presentations to citizens' groups to provide information on emergency plans and their implementation processes.", "TaskType": "Core", "task_importance_score": 3.55, "penetration": 0.0}, {"ONETSOCCode": "11-9161", "Task": "Study emergency plans used elsewhere to gather information for plan development.", "TaskType": "Core", "task_importance_score": 3.09, "penetration": 0.0}, {"ONETSOCCode": "11-9161", "Task": "Collaborate with other officials to prepare and analyze damage assessments following disasters or emergencies.", "TaskType": "Core", "task_importance_score": 4.09, "penetration": 0.0}, {"ONETSOCCode": "11-9161", "Task": "Inspect facilities and equipment, such as emergency management centers and communications equipment, to determine their operational and functional capabilities in emergency situations.", "TaskType": "Core", "task_importance_score": 4.05, "penetration": 0.0}, {"ONETSOCCode": "11-9161", "Task": "Conduct surveys to determine the types of emergency-related needs to be addressed in disaster planning, or provide technical support to others conducting such surveys.", "TaskType": "Core", "task_importance_score": 3.9, "penetration": 0.0}, {"ONETSOCCode": "11-9161", "Task": "Consult with officials of local and area governments, schools, hospitals, and other institutions to determine their needs and capabilities in the event of a natural disaster or other emergency.", "TaskType": "Core", "task_importance_score": 4.64, "penetration": 0.0}, {"ONETSOCCode": "11-9161", "Task": "Prepare emergency situation status reports that describe response and recovery efforts, needs, and preliminary damage assessments.", "TaskType": "Core", "task_importance_score": 4.36, "penetration": 0.0}, {"ONETSOCCode": "11-9161", "Task": "Review emergency plans of individual organizations, such as medical facilities, to ensure their adequacy.", "TaskType": "Core", "task_importance_score": 4.0, "penetration": 0.0}, {"ONETSOCCode": "11-9161", "Task": "Develop and maintain liaisons with municipalities, county departments, and similar entities to facilitate plan development, response effort coordination, and exchanges of personnel and equipment.", "TaskType": "Core", "task_importance_score": 4.48, "penetration": 0.0}, {"ONETSOCCode": "11-9161", "Task": "Propose alteration of emergency response procedures, based on regulatory changes, technological changes, or knowledge gained from outcomes of previous emergency situations.", "TaskType": "Core", "task_importance_score": 3.67, "penetration": 0.0}, {"ONETSOCCode": "11-9161", "Task": "Inventory and distribute nuclear, biological, and chemical detection and contamination equipment, providing instruction in its maintenance and use.", "TaskType": "Supplemental", "task_importance_score": 2.67, "penetration": 0.0}, {"ONETSOCCode": "11-9161", "Task": "Provide communities with assistance in applying for federal funding for emergency management facilities, radiological instrumentation, and related items.", "TaskType": "Core", "task_importance_score": 3.35, "penetration": 0.0}, {"ONETSOCCode": "11-9161", "Task": "Prepare plans that outline operating procedures to be used in response to disasters or emergencies, such as hurricanes, nuclear accidents, and terrorist attacks, and in recovery from these events.", "TaskType": "Core", "task_importance_score": 4.29, "penetration": 0.0}, {"ONETSOCCode": "11-9161", "Task": "Develop and perform tests and evaluations of emergency management plans in accordance with state and federal regulations.", "TaskType": "Core", "task_importance_score": 4.14, "penetration": 0.0}, {"ONETSOCCode": "11-9161", "Task": "Train local groups in the preparation of long-term plans that are compatible with federal and state plans.", "TaskType": "Core", "task_importance_score": 3.3